statements: SELECT * FROM athlete_biomechanical_parameters;
SELECT athlete_id, name, age FROM athlete_biomechanical_parameters WHERE age > 25;
SELECT name, weight FROM athlete_biomechanical_parameters WHERE weight < 70;
SELECT athlete_id, height FROM athlete_biomechanical_parameters WHERE athlete_id = 3;
SELECT * FROM athlete_biomechanical_parameters ORDER BY height DESC;
SELECT * FROM athlete_biomechanical_parameters WHERE age > 25 ORDER BY height ASC;
SELECT athlete_id, name, weight FROM athlete_biomechanical_parameters WHERE weight < 70 AND stride_length > 1.5;
SELECT DISTINCT name FROM athlete_biomechanical_parameters WHERE weight BETWEEN 60 AND 80;
SELECT * FROM athlete_biomechanical_parameters WHERE age >= 20 AND age <= 30 ORDER BY age DESC, height DESC;
SELECT athlete_id, name, age, weight FROM athlete_biomechanical_parameters WHERE age > 18 AND age < 35 AND weight > 50 ORDER BY age;
SELECT * FROM biomechanical_parameters;
SELECT athlete_id, height, weight FROM biomechanical_parameters WHERE gender = 'Male';
SELECT athlete_id, age, gender FROM biomechanical_parameters ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT * FROM performance_analysis WHERE analysis_id = 1;
SELECT athlete_id, performance_score FROM performance_analysis WHERE date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM biomechanical_parameters WHERE height > 180 ORDER BY weight DESC, age ASC;
SELECT athlete_id, SUM(weight) AS total_weight FROM biomechanical_parameters GROUP BY athlete_id HAVING total_weight > 75;
SELECT athlete_id, performance_score, date FROM performance_analysis WHERE DATE(date) = '2022-01-01' ORDER BY performance_score DESC;
SELECT athlete_id, gender FROM biomechanical_parameters WHERE age BETWEEN 20 AND 30 AND gender = 'Male';

SELECT biomechanical_parameters.*, performance_score FROM biomechanical_parameters JOIN performance_analysis ON biomechanical_parameters.athlete_id = performance_analysis.athlete_id WHERE performance_score > 8.5;
SELECT * FROM biomechanical_parameters WHERE athlete_id = 1;
SELECT parameter_name, parameter_value FROM biomechanical_parameters WHERE athlete_id = 2;

SELECT * FROM biomechanical_parameters WHERE parameter_name = 'Strength'
SELECT athlete_id, parameter_name, parameter_value FROM biomechanical_parameters WHERE parameter_value > 50 ORDER BY athlete_id ASC
SELECT athlete_id, name, age, height, weight FROM athlete_personal_info WHERE age BETWEEN 20 AND 30 ORDER BY height DESC
SELECT athlete_id, date, analysis_result FROM performance_analysis WHERE date >= '2021-01-01' ORDER BY date DESC
SELECT DISTINCT athlete_id, name FROM athlete_personal_info JOIN performance_analysis ON athlete_personal_info.athlete_id = performance_analysis.athlete_id
SELECT * FROM Athletes;
SELECT name, age FROM Athletes ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT id, name, weight FROM Athletes WHERE weight > 70;
SELECT measurement_id, athlete_id, date FROM Measurements WHERE date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
SELECT a.name, p.speed FROM Athletes a INNER JOIN Performance p ON a.id = p.athlete_id;
SELECT name, age, weight FROM Athletes;
SELECT * FROM Measurements WHERE date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-03-31';

SELECT Athletes.name, Measurements.date, Performance.speed FROM Athletes JOIN Measurements ON Athletes.id = Measurements.athlete_id JOIN Performance ON Measurements.measurement_id = Performance.measurement_id WHERE Performance.speed > 10.00;

SELECT Athletes.name, Measurements.date, Performance.speed, Analysis.result FROM Athletes JOIN Measurements ON Athletes.id = Measurements.athlete_id JOIN Performance ON Measurements.measurement_id = Performance.measurement_id JOIN Analysis ON Performance.performance_id = Analysis.performance_id WHERE Analysis.result = 'Excellent';

SELECT Athletes.id, Athletes.name, Measurements.date, Performance.speed, Performance.endurance FROM Athletes JOIN Measurements ON Athletes.id = Measurements.athlete_id JOIN Performance ON Measurements.measurement_id = Performance.measurement_id WHERE Performance.speed > 10.00 AND Performance.endurance > 8.00 ORDER BY Performance.speed DESC, Performance.endurance ASC;
